Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.12,0:20:06.56,Main,hina,0,0,0,,ナン…キョウ…ク
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.64,0:20:28.72,Main,kima,0,0,0,,どうする？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:33.02,Main,hina,0,0,0,,報瀬、先行けよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:39.09,Main,kima,0,0,0,,どうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:50.35,Main,all,0,0,0,,せーのっ！
